<h1>Your Visa Letter is Ready!</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @participant.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Great news! Your visa letter application for <strong><%= @event.name %></strong> has been approved.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @download_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ec3750; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">
    Download Your Visa Letter (PDF)
  </a>
</p>

<p><small>Or copy this link: <%= @download_url %></small></p>

<h2>Event Details</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Event:</strong> <%= @event.name %></li>
  <li><strong>Dates:</strong> <%= @event.date_range %></li>
  <li><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @event.full_address %></li>
  <li><strong>Reference Number:</strong> <%= @application.reference_number %></li>
</ul>

<h2>Next Steps</h2>
<p>Please print this letter and include it with your visa application. If you have any questions or need additional documentation, please contact us at <%= @event.contact_email %>.</p>

<p>We look forward to seeing you at <%= @event.name %>!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Hack Club Team</p>
